videos.description: Minnesota's Shannon Brooks grabs the hand-off from Demry Croft and rushes into the end zone for a short 2-yard touchdown against Oregon State.
videos.headline: Golden Gophers continue rowing to big lead

videos.description: Minnesota RB Shannon Brooks snags his second rushing touchdown in the third quarter to extend the lead over Oregon State.
videos.headline: Golden Gopher barrels into end zone

videos.description: Minnesota RB Shannon Brooks bounces into the end zone and earns his third rushing touchdown to give the Golden Gophers a 41-14 lead over the Beavers.
videos.headline: Brooks scores third rushing TD for Minnesota
